    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n3669" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπι-χέω</span></b> , aor. 1 <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπέχευε</span>, inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπιχεῦαι</span>, mid. aor. 1 <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπεχεύατο</span>, aor. 2 <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπέχυντο</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">pour upon, heap up</span>, mid. (aor.
          1), for oneself; not of liquids only, but of earth, leaves, etc.;
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πολλὴν δ᾽ ἐπεχεύατο ὕ̄λην</span>, for
          wattling, <i><span class="en">Od. 5.257</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; χύσιν φύλλων</span>, for a bed, <i><span class="en">Od. 5.487</span></i>; mid., aor. 2, intr. (metaph.)
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τοὶ δ᾽ ἐπέχυντο</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">poured
            in</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 15.654</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 16.295</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
